#. [side]: type=Outlaw, id=Urza Nalmath
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/02_Proven_by_the_Sword.cfg:99
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/02_Proven_by_the_Sword.cfg:100
