msgstr "淚滴谷"

#. [side]: type=Dark Adept, type=Dark Sorcerer, type=Dark Sorcerer, id=Mal A'kai
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/04_Vale_of_Tears.cfg:60
